6.6 STANDARDS FOR PROVIDED CONTENT: Both TheMart and i-Escrow retain the right to supply content that:
(a) does not unintentionally infringe upon any third party's copyright, patent, trademark, trade secret, or rights of publicity or privacy;
(b) complies with all applicable laws, statutes, ordinances, and regulations (excluding those pertaining to export control, unfair competition, antidiscrimination, or false advertising);
(c) is not libelous, defamatory, unlawfully threatening, or harassing;
(d) is neither obscene nor harmful to minors, but does not necessarily exclude content suitable for mature audiences;
(e) does not include any harmful computer programming routines intended to damage, interfere with, surreptitiously intercept, or expropriate any system, data, or personal information; and
(f) is truthful, accurate, and while striving for accuracy, may contain minor inconsistencies or errors.
